text.title: mod_int
text.tspan: Study Under a Master ◾ Shop / Procure ◾ Craft an Item
✔✔ 3 questions from the list ✔ 2 questions from the list
✷ Recently? ✷ About to? ✷ Lookout for? ✷ Useful/valuable? ✷ Control? ✷ False?
✔✔ Choose ✔ Deal your fatigue and the foe attacks you
✗ Deal 1 fatigue and the foe attacks you
✷ Deal fatigue and avoid the foe's attack ✷ Double your fatigue dice
✔/✗ Provide immediate and concrete assurance of your promise
✔/✗ Stumble, hesitate, or flinch - worse outcome, hard bargain, or ugly choice
✔✔ GM tells you something interesting and useful
✔/✗ GM tells you something interesting, it's on you to make it useful
✔✔ 3 green tokens on Defend ✔ 2 green tokens ✗ 1 green token
✷ Redirect the attack to yourself ✷ Halve the attack's effect
✷ Open up the attacker to an ally +1 ✷ Deal 1 fatigue to the attacker
✔✔ Deal fatigue ✔ Choose, and deal fatigue ✗ GM chooses, deal fatigue
✷ Move to get the shot (GM's choice of danger)
✷ Reduce fatigue dealt ✷ Use ammo - subtract 1 from Equipment
✔✔ Find a safe spot / avoid attention. Recover 1d4
✔ Recover 1d4. The foe moves ✗ Recover 1. The foe moves
As long as you're not cornered or surrounded, escape your foes.
Spend 1 green token and 1 Equipment and say what you brought along to help
